title: [SOLVED]820-3435 no power/dim green light
message:
Hello, I have a 820-3435 that came in with no power. It was missing PPBUS_G3H (0v). After replacing ISL6259 I was able to get a dim green light but still no power.  PPBUS_G3H is still missing. any suggestions? Im stuck

Thanks,

title: [SOLVED]820-3435 no power/dim green light
message:
1) Is PP3V42_G3H present?
2) What is the resistance to ground on PPBUS_G3H?
3) What is the resistance between pins 17/18 of U7100?
4) What is the resistance between pins 27/28 of U7100?

title: [SOLVED]820-3435 no power/dim green light
message: And what should the resistance be between pins 27/28?

title: [SOLVED]820-3435 no power/dim green light
message:
It should be 20 Oms. I got correct reading after replacing the current sense resistors. 

R7005 was bad. I was only getting 1.73v on CHGR_DCIN. I replaced it with a donor and got a working macbook

You can close this post. Thanks!
